They say marriage is like a walk in the park, but it's Jurassic Park. Some of us will endure, but others choose to let our marriage go extinct. Christel Du Toit has written a book about how to ‘divorce smart’. She tells us more. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Christel Du Toit has written a book about how to divorce smart. She says the book is about making small financial decisions before and after you divorce in order to rebuild your financial life. READ: Dubai suspends marriage and divorce during virus lockdown She says the book will guide the reader not to make bad financial decisions. Du Toit shares more details about her book in the video above.